ase and includes soft potential kernels. More\nimportantly, for the Dirichlet boundary condition, this work strengthens the\nconvergence so as to make the boundary layer visible. This answers an open\nproblem proposed by Ukai \\cite{Ukai}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Oct 2015 20:56:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-13"}
